Inclusion Criteria:

* Female patients aged ≥18 years and ≤75 years;
* ECOG performance status of 0-2;
* Histologically confirmed HR-positive/HER2-positive advanced breast cancer:
* Definition of HER2 positivity: IHC 3+ or IHC 2+/ISH positive prior to T-DXd treatment;
* Definition of HR positivity:

Inclusion Criteria:

* Patients who can voluntarily sign an informed consent form;
* Females aged ≥18 years old when signing the informed consent form;
* ECOG PS physical status score of 0 to 2 points;
* Histologically confirmed HER2-positive metastatic breast cancer patients; Note: HER2 positivity
